<HEADLINE> Chinese Vice-Premier Meets Madagascar Minister </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, June 18 (Xinhua) -- Chinese Vice-Premier Li Lanqing,
in a meeting with Madagascar's Minister of Industrialization and
Handicrafts Manasse Esoavelomandroso here today, expressed his
sincere hope that all African nations will be politically stable
and experience economic growth.
