Run series to prepare for her next international marathon race in
Tokyo on November 30.
</P>
<P>
Dundee-based McColgan, who won the gold medal at the 1991 world
championships in Tokyo, spoke of her relief at her successful
operation.
</P>
<P>
McColgan said she felt that she would not be ready for the
world championship 10,000m trial at Sheffield on June 29 so soon
after surgery. 
