75 percent of the required amount for each development project.
The rural finance program will provide loans to be paid back with
interest.
</P>
<P>
Grants and loans will be given to people who will form
cooperatives and set up ginning industries,irrigation systems and
fish ponds to be run on a commercial basis in the province.
</P>
<P>
This will help distribute development evenly which has been in
the past concentrated in urban areas, added Ngulube. 
