<TEXT>
<P>
ROME, June 17 (Xinhua) -- The Italian government coalition
split today in the Lower House over an opposition motion defending
the performance of the Italian armed forces in Somalia, while
urging a government probe into misconduct by individual soldiers.
</P>
<P>
