<HEADLINE> Yugoslavia, Italy Sign Cultural Accord </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BELGRADE, June 17 (Xinhua) -- Yugoslavia and Italy signed an
accord here today in order to further strengthen their cultural
exchanges and cooperation between 1997 and 2000, the Yugoslav news
agency Tanjug reported.
</P>
<P>
