Dressed in military uniform, Koroma said after the ceremony
that he would perform his duties to the best of his ability.
</P>
<P>
He said he was fully committed to bring lasting peace to
Sierra Leone and return the country to a democratically elected
government.
</P>
<P>
"I hope the international community would help my government
consolidate the peace already achieved'', he added. 
