attention to the existing refugee problem in the Horn of Africa
which seems to be "overshadowed by new emergencies in other parts
of the world".
</P>
<P>
David Lambo, UNHCR regional liaison representative for Africa,
on his part said the present African refugees' situation is
promising as a number of them are returning to their respective
homeland.
</P>
<P>
